95
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:34,200
...no meio de toda esta porcaria.

96
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,300
Ela está só.

97
00:10:37,700 --> 00:10:39,000
Eles...

98
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,900
...não podem...

99
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,800
... tocar...

100
